.SS uint32 Position [readonly]
.sp
Playback position in milliseconds.
.sp
Changing the position may generate additional events that will be sent to the
remote device. When position is 0 it means the track is starting and when it\(aqs
greater than or equal to track\(aqs duration the track has ended.
.sp
Note that even if duration is not available in metadata it\(aqs possible to signal
its end by setting position to the maximum uint32 value.
